{"tid":1444632,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我地唔可以輸，要打好文宣要改變策略，求入尼睇睇","createTime":"2019-08-11T12:55:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T13:39:51.000Z","uid":231818,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"51fb5c25511f68c9e1979646ed6f2b1484644bf1","tid":1444632,"uid":231818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:55:33.000Z","msg":"我地今次輸就永遠都輸<br />\n但中共港共已經開始反攻<br />\n我地都要調整策略<br />\n<br />\n當日我地令政府暫緩<br />\n唔止因為我地遊行集會<br />\n仲因為我地肯擺脫同温層<br />\n向廢老廢中埋手<br />\n係因為我地有無限創意<br />\n做左一件又一件令政府措手不及嘅事<br />\n<br />\n同我地冇淨係勇武<br />\n我地有和理非勇武合作<br />\n個公式係：<br />\n和理非&gt;期限&gt;勇武<br />\n但而家已經係勇武勇武勇武<br />\n明明和理非嘅活動<br />\n最後都變勇武<br />\n我知大家好嬲<br />\n但唔好比仇恨怒火影響<br />\n要冷靜<br />\n記住，和理非代表嘅民意係勇武最大嘅支持<br />\n<br />\n仲有<br />\n係時侯停勇武一兩星期<br />\n比勇武休息<br />\n同冷靜落尼調整策略<br />\n大家唔好急<br />\n尼場係一場漫長嘅抗爭<br />\n急只會令我地出錯<br />\n<br />\n我地係時間跳出同温層<br />\n再次向建制支持者向廢中廢老埋手<br />\n向全世界做國際文宣<br />\n<br />\n大家要記住<br />\n我地輸<br />\n就無得翻身"},{"pid":"5fdaf2a584e310ceedf8d85ae541d4c8b7984093","tid":1444632,"uid":231818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:57:03.000Z","msg":"之前開過啲文宣post<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HEz2fVg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHEz2fVg.jpg&h=3e180186&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ce74b3401cd9698acda4300826225f976dffd573","tid":1444632,"uid":231818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:57:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SJK2fVq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSJK2fVq.jpg&h=05ba91f5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e099f9cceeac0275740588e77ce1d652e658be07","tid":1444632,"uid":231818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:57:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SeakM19.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSeakM19.jpg&h=1586121f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fba0fe30cf88d005294ad151ca0a9deb8b453e26",